1
00:01:59,479 --> 00:02:00,120
Actually,

2
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,330
I am still somewhat useful.

3
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,000
Don't be afraid.

4
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,600
Princess,

5
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,200
I'll protect you.

6
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,220
Good dogs don't block the way.

7
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,120
He's getting anxious.

8
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:52,960
In that case,

9
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,060
you really won't die in there.

10
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,200
If that's the case,

11
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,040
hurry up and go in,

12
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:00,880
and die again.

13
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,600
Don't you know you told me

14
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,560
that entering the virtual space

15
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,960
would have severe side effects?

16
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,200
And in severe cases,

17
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,640
it causes mental confusion,

18
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,880
loss of consciousness,

19
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,080
or even turning into a vegetable.

20
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:13,840
Don't worry.

21
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,960
You'll be fine for twenty minutes.

22
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,690
Then why don't you go yourself?

23
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:19,360
If I could go in,

24
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,720
I wouldn't need you to take the risk.

25
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:22,960
Fine.

26
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:23,850
Then,

27
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,640
I quit.

28
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:25,400
Wait.

29
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,040
Think carefully.

30
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,040
If you leave here,

31
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:29,000
can you really find

32
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,730
a decent job?

33
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:32,520
Even if I have to sweep streets,

34
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,560
deliver packages,

35
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,690
or deliver takeout,

36
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,760
I won't risk my life for you here anymore.

37
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:38,280
Tch.

38
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,800
How did it go?

39
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,320
Let me do it.

40
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,320
Same as before.

41
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,800
Found nothing.

42
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,760
No, I meant how are you feeling?

43
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,520
I'm fine.

44
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,160
Dad.

45
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,440
I think we were wrong.

46
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,519
That prince

47
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:18,769
doesn't seem like he's here to kill me.

48
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,620
No wonder we couldn't find any clues.

49
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:27,000
Maybe there was more to it back then.

50
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,159
Let's try again.

51
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,040
Are you crazy?

52
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,480
If you enter virtual space continuously,

53
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,240
your brain will fry.

54
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,500
I'll handle it.

55
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,560
You get some rest.

56
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,440
Wait for me.

57
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:53,130
(Thai) There are fluctuations in the virtual space.

58
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:01,560
(Thai) Something is moving.

59
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,480
Where did that brat Liu Yu

60
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,360
run off to?

61
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,480
Liu Yu!

62
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,600
Pay up!

63
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,480
Spread out.

64
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,560
Liu Yu!

65
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,160
Liu Yu! Pay up!

66
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,440
You want money?

67
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,300
Come and get it.

68
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,520
Don't come any closer.

69
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,560
You just want money, right?

70
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,240
Here you go.

71
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:08,920
We've been tricked.

72
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,560
After him!

73
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,200
Don't let that brat get away.

74
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,200
I just owe you some money.

75
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,080
Even the great Zhuge Liang lost battles.

76
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:21,880
It's venture capital.

77
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:22,810
Don't you get it?

78
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,580
No memberships, no spending.

79
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:31,440
I'm not interested in anything.

80
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,640
If this is a shakedown, I can't pay a cent.

81
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,640
And I don't want to provide any services.

82
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,440
Liu Yu.

83
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,420
I'm here to give you money.

84
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:40,760
I know.

85
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,280
You give me money

86
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:43,480
to send me to my death.

87
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,680
My life is worth a lot.

88
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,159
Tell your Professor Wei.

89
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:48,220
He can't afford it.

90
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,320
While you were gone,

91
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:53,650
the professor did interview many people.

92
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,520
But none of them could handle

93
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,240
the pressure of the virtual space.

94
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:57,920
So,

95
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,680
we need you, Liu Yu.

96
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:01,520
Come on.

97
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,300
Changed your mind?

98
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,680
I appreciate the sentiment.

99
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,160
But do me one last favor.

100
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:16,720
What favor?

101
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,200
Liu Yu.

102
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,560
I paid back the five million I owed you.

103
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,400
We're even now.
